* Address the pygame Sprite Group Z-Depth problem. Right now sprites and lasers are being drawn in arbitrary z-order.
* Event Dispatch system. This will allow entities to trigger animations and UI widgets to receive input events.
* Queued Animation effects. Then Damage Numbers and Damage Animations can be dispatched in sequence.
* Prerender of all surfarray effects to improve cpu performance.
* Remove actions in place for queued eventmanager events
* Use config file to store many of the constants in viewer
* First round / battlestart round ship entrance/warp in animations